OL,5,G1800 Antiques Roadshow
OL,6,     FManchester 1: Fiona Bruce and the
OL,7,     Fexperts visit Manchester Town
OL,8,     FHall, where items awaiting
OL,9,     Fvaluation include a chair that
OL,10,     FArthur Negus examined on the show
OL,11,     F30 years earlier.
OL,12,G1900 Dom Chinea's Cornish Workshop
OL,13,     FDom tries out water dowsing so he
OL,14,     Fcan fill his new pond. He and
OL,15,     Fengineer friend Sam Lovegrove fix
OL,16,     Fsome church bells and then put a
OL,17,     Fsurf lifesaving club's quad bike
OL,18,     Fback on the beach.
